{
  "stem": "14613.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so there were five boys left out of the 805 boys that were brought in from all the camps together.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The rest?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "What happened?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The reason they called us back to the appellplatz is because it came a transport from Auschwitz of grown-ups.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So they took the grown-ups which came from Auschwitz to work, and they sent all the children back to Auschwitz to crematoria.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Why did they leave the five people?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "According to the Germans, everything has to be in ordnung, in order.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "What happened?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They have sent 800 grown-ups.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And therefore, they had to send back 800 children so everything would be in order.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "This is how five of the children were left, while all the 800 went to Auschwitz to die.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[DRINKS] How much more time after this do you think your spent in Gross Rosen?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Again, exactly, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we spent a few months.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in a way, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] for us-- for the five boys-- we had a little better time in this camp.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because we were then sent as [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we were sent mostly to, to stay in the barracks, to clean the barracks, to work around the barracks.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So that was a great privilege, because all the rest of them were grown-ups.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were the only youngsters.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] from there, we were sent to what I would say our last camp, which was Flossenburg.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Flossenburg is also in the Bavaria in Germany.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this was a camp which was really, in a way, a working camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At least, part of the camps was working camp, except for few of the, few barracks, which were not for work.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
